Original Voxyne/Rahu-Ketu byte-level model framing and sigma_K integration by
Ramakrishnan. The implementation uses standard Transformer layers as building
blocks. The byte-level zero-free representation, sigma_K control path, and model
framing are Voxyne-specific. No third-party source code is included.

